Metracker

A guard for your database.

Capture metrics, limit connections, and protect your database from
suspicious queries. That’s what Metracker offers.

Repository structure:

./example/db  
Example database used for testing.

./build.sh  
Script to build the CLI.

./interceptor  
The core of Metracker. Responsible for creating and managing the database interceptor.

./user/jsonsave.go  
Handles persistence of user data in JSON format.